data.description: Look no further!  This home has it all!  Only 2 years old, this beautiful 2-story home has 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths with attached 2-car garage, fenced in back yard, and is partially secluded as it sits on a deadend street.  The first floor features a formal living room/office/study, ½ bath, and has a spacious/open great room with fireplace which is open to the bright dining/kitchen area.  The kitchen boasts tons of cabinets, a pantry for additional storage, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and an island.  Right off the dining area, you may venture out to the gorgeous, screened patio area which overlook the large fenced private backyard.  Now travel to the second level of the home to find the enormous primary bedroom and bath with walk in closet and double vanity, 3 additional good-sized bedrooms, a full bath, and the convenient laundry room.  Seller will also pay $1000 in closing costs/prepaids to the Buyer at closing!
